<html>
<div>
	<h1>Your group was updated!</h1>
	<p>This email is to inform you that your group information was updated:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Phone: <%= phone %></li>
		<li>Email: <%= email %></li>
		<li>PIN: <%= pin %></li>
	</ul>
	<p>Your group members are:</p>
	<ul>
		<% people.forEach(function(person){ %>
		<li><%= person.name %></li>
		<% }); %>
	</ul>
	<h2>Reminder: How to Check In</h2>
	<p>When you attend an event, find the venue code for where you are attending (this should be posted at the
		entrance) and click the link below to start the check-in process.</p>
	<ul>
		<li><a href="<%= url %>"><%= url %></a></li>
	</ul>
	<p>Remember, you will need the PIN you selected to complete your check-in, so save this message for reference
		later.</p>
</div>

</html>